{"lemma":"شَعْث","slug":"شَعْث","root":"ش.ع.ث","root_slug":"ش-ع-ث","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ع-ث","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22450","n22453","n22454","n22455"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D8%AB"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22450","headword_ar":"شَعِثَ","root":"$Ev","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEavN","text_ar":"شَعَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(hair)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, shaggy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dishevelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and frouzy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altered in odour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in consequence of its being seldom dressed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, defiled with dust, and matted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compacted, in consequence of its being seldom anointed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or, accord. to El-Ghooree,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it wanted oil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ointment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 50:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$E~t","text_ar":"تشعّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [the same: or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, matted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compacted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and dusty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And the former verb, [and app. ↓ the latter also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the head)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dusty, not being renovated"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by dressing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anointing"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor cleansed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) Also the former verb, aor. as above, (L, K, and Ham p. 469,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEavN","text_ar":"شَعَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K, and Ham) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEuwvapN","text_ar":"شُعُوثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L and Ham,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, shaggy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dishevelled, in the hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JM, PS,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and frouzy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altered in odour, in consequence of its being seldom dressed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JM:) or it signifies (or signifies also, JM)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a dusty head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K, JM,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and plucked hair, unanointed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had matted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compacted, and dusty, hair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, and Ham p. 469:) and in like manner ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$E~v","text_ar":"تشعّث","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEavN","text_ar":"شَعَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$aE~uvN","text_ar":"تَشَعُّثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) [or each,] also signifies (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being separated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disunited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spread out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompacted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as is the head of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siwaAk","text_ar":"سِوَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tooth-stick, by its being bruised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mangled by blows"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^osu Als~iwaAki","text_ar":"رَاْسُ السِّوَاكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$E~v","text_ar":"تشعّث","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwatidi","text_ar":"الوَتِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The head of the tooth-stick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the wooden peg"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stake, became disintegrated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separated, disunited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompacted, in its component parts"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its fibres;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered brushy; by its being bruised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mangled by blows"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$E~vwA","text_ar":"تشعّثوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning men]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became separated, disunited, dispersed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scattered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEiva","text_ar":"شَعِثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above, (TK,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEavN","text_ar":"شَعَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of the state of affairs, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dissolved, broken up, discomposed, deranged, disorganized, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, * K, * TA, TK. [In the S and A and K, this is placed as the first of all the meanings in this art.; and in the A, it is mentioned among the meanings that are proper, not tropical; but in my opinion it is tropical. See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEavN","text_ar":"شَعَثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.])"}],"source_refs":["Msb","A","Mgh","K","TA","JM","PS","S","L","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n22453","headword_ar":"شَعْثٌ","root":"$Ev","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n22454","headword_ar":"شَعَثٌ","root":"$Ev","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of 1 [q. v.]. (L, Msb, &c.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lam~a A@ll~`hu $aEavaka","text_ar":"لَمَّ ا@للّٰهُ شَعَثَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEavakumo","text_ar":"شَعَثَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) i. e. (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God rectify,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repair, and consolidate, what is discomposed, deranged, disorganized, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled, of thy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"your, affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lm","text_ar":"لم"},{"kind":"text","text":";) or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consolidate thy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"your, disorganized, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled, state of affairs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A: * [in the latter expressly distinguished as tropical:]) [and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEovaka","text_ar":"شَعْثَكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEovakumo","text_ar":"شَعْثَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; perhaps by poetic license; for] Kaab Ibn-Málik El-Ansáree says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"lam~a A@loA_il`hu bihK $aEovFA waram~a bihi\n                      \n                     \n                        A^umuwra A^um~atihi waAlA^amoru munota$iru"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God rectified and consolidated, by him, a discomposed, deranged, disorganized, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled, state of affairs, and repaired, by him, the affairs of his people, when the state of affairs was broken up"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) It is said in a trad., as a form of prayer,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoA^aluka raHomapF talum~u bihaA $aEaviY","text_ar":"اَسْاَلُكَ رَحْمَةً تَلُمُّ بِهَا شَعَثِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I ask of Thee mercy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereby thou shalt consolidate what is discomposed, deranged, disorganized, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled, of my state of affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A"]},{"entry_id":"n22455","headword_ar":"شَعِثٌ","root":"$Ev","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to hair,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shaggy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dishevelled:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shaggy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dishevelled, and frouzy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altered in odour, in consequence of its being seldom dressed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1, first sentence:)] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defiled with dust, and matted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compacted, in consequence of its being seldom anointed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And in a similar sense applied to the head of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misowaAk","text_ar":"مِسْوَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or tooth-stick, meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disintegrated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separated, disunited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompacted, in its fibres;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered brushy; by its being bruised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; and so as applied to the head of a wooden peg or stake; as indicated by an explanation of its verb]. (MA.) [And in the TA it is applied to a plant, as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Straggling."},{"kind":"text","text":"] See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oEavu","text_ar":"اَشْعَثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dirty in the body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["MA"]}]}}